_sText:
This map is based on my beta of heli_attack which is not likely to be published. This one however, has extended sewers and 2 bomb sites.

Features:
Overview
Nav file with area names
soundscape
custom materials

Story:
Terrorists want to attack a high-tech research facility as a result of political and diplomatical failures between goverments and terrorist organisations. The facility has been evacuated immediately and a team of higly trained members of various Counter-Terrorist corps have been send to face the crysis...

Many thanks to Nay0r for his help, support and ideas. I owe you a beer buddy. :)

HAVE FUN!
